Known clans among the Nine Wei included:
* The [[Fan clan]], a Wei clan with close ties to the Nine Golden Swords as of the late 15{{th}} century DR.{{Cite organized play/LFR/Falling Snow, White Petal|4}} 
* The [[Neng clan]], the most influential of the Wei clans owing to their connections to imperial [[Shou Lung]], and thus the leader among the Nine. The head of the clan was said to be a "walking [[god]]".
